    "1ed4ee22-f4e4-4956-9271-75427ba6965c": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "template--14915046801497__1ed4ee22-f4e4-4956-9271-75427ba6965c-168620152661341c1c-1": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ment_snow.jpg",
            "rating": 5,
            "title": "Functional fashion",
            "text": "<p>I love my Mentawai suit in Snow! It fits like a glove and works wonders both in small waves and bigger days. The suit stays on and looks great at the same time. When you don’t have to worry about bikinis flying off in the whitewash, you can focus more on riding waves. I love functional fashion and OSB nails it! Hope to get more colors soon 😍</p>",
            "author": "Katherine Matias",
            "button_text": "{{ collection.title }}",
            "link": "shopify://products/sustainable-short-sleeve-swimsuit-white"
          }
        },
        "template--14915046801497__1ed4ee22-f4e4-4956-9271-75427ba6965c-168620152661341c1c-0": {
          "type": "product",
          "settings": {
            "product": "sustainable-swimwear-mentawai-olive",
            "show_second_image": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "title": "I'm in love",
            "text": "<p>I really liked the way this suit fits, slimming my figure.  I have seen many similar models, but here the fabric is of the highest quality.  You don't have to worry about your swimsuit coming off during a wipeout.  And after surfing you can effectively unzip your chest and go drink a coconut 🥥</p>",
            "author": "Elizaveta Bogatyreva (Tabanan, ID)",
            "show_product_title": true,
            "button_text": "View product"
          }
        }
      },
