    "image_with_text_6b4DHK": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/MG_7761_Last_Resort_Federico_Vanno_Liquid_Barrel_copy.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Why Ocean Soul Surfing Swimsuits Are Different",
        "text": "<p><strong> Surf Swimwear That Stays Put</strong></p><p>We’ve all been there - pulling at straps or worrying about your suit mid-session. Our surfing swimsuits are designed with secure fits, non-slip designs, and double-lining to give you confidence in every wave. No shifting. No sagging. No distractions.</p><p>Long sleeve swimsuits for maximum sun safety<br/></p><p>Supportive one pieces for performance and style<br/></p><p>Surf bikinis that combine minimal bulk with maximum hold</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
