        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "UPF 50+ Sun Protection",
        "text": "<p>Long hours in the surf mean high sun exposure. All our surf swimwear is made with UPF 50+ fabric for built-in skin protection. Our womens rash guards and long sleeve surf suits give you extra coverage without overheating - ideal for tropical conditions or full-day surf trips.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
