        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainable & Ethical",
        "text": "<p>Made from Econyl® recycled fabric, our suits help clean the ocean by turning discarded fishing nets and plastic waste into luxury swimwear. Every piece is:</p><p>Designed to last twice as long as standard suits<br/></p><p>Made in small batches to reduce waste<br/></p><p>Ethically produced in Bali with fair wages</p>",
